<br>
metal bits <br>
2 small pieces of ore (stackable), flask water <br>
Trivial at 18<br>
<br>
studs<br>
3 metal bits, file, flask water (yield 2)<br>
Trivial at 35<br>
<br>
skinning knife <br>
dagger blade mold, hilt mold, small brick of ore, water (used in tailoring) <br>
trivial at 41<br>
<br>
pot <br>
metal bits, pot mold, standing legs mold, flask water <br>
trivial at 50<br>
<br>
forged bastard sword <br>
water, sheet metal, pommel mold, hilt mold, dual edged blade mold  <br>
trivial at 68<br>
<br>
filleting knife <br>
3 metal bits, scaler mold, water<br>
trivial at 76<br>
<br>
banded gorget<br>
sheet of metal (2 small bricks of ore, flask water ), gorget mold, water flask<br>
trivial at 92<br>
<br>
banded leggings<br>
3 sheets of metal, leggings mold, water flask<br>
trivial at 108<br>
<br>
banded tunic<br>
3 sheets of metal, mail mold, water flask<br>
trivial at 115<br>
<br>
embroidering needle <br>
needle mold, metal bits, celestial essence, flask water <br>
trivial 122<br>
<br>
Thats as far as I know... for more info I suggest contacting Calanae.<br>
